# Google Maps API Configuration
# Get this from Google Cloud Console (https://console.cloud.google.com)
# Enable the Maps Embed API in your Google Cloud project
# No API key is required for Google Maps Embed API (iframe embeds)
# But if you want to use the Static Street View API, you'll need an API key:
# VITE_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here

# ChatBot AI Configuration
# Choose ONE API provider below for the AI ChatBot assistant

# Option 1: ChatGPT API (OpenAI)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# Option 2: Google Gemini API
# Get your API key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# NOTE: 
# - Keep your API keys private and never commit them to version control
# - Copy this file to .env.local and add your actual API key
# - Only one API key should be active at a time
# - For production, consider using a backend proxy to hide API keys
